import { feedback } from '../data/feedback'
import { Grid, Card, CardHeader, Avatar, CardContent, Typography } from '@mui/material'

const Feedback = () => (
  <>
    <Typography variant="h4" mt={5} mb={3}>Feedback</Typography>
    <Grid container spacing={4}>
      {feedback.map((f) => (
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={f.name}>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader
              avatar={<Avatar src={f.image} />}
              title={f.name}
              subheader={f.project}
            />
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="body2">"{f.quote}"</Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      ))}
    </Grid>
  </>
)

export default Feedback
